      <title>新加坡要求奢侈品卖家在洗钱丑闻后采取更多行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/singapore-demands-luxury-sellers-do-more-after-laundering-fiasco</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为该国打击洗钱举措的一部分，新加坡呼吁该国的房地产经纪人、宝石经销商和豪华汽车销售商更加主动地标记可疑客户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/singapore-demands-luxury-sellers-do-more-after-laundering-fiasco</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国核监督机构对乌克兰核电站停电发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/iaea-cites-deep-concern-over-supply-at-ukraine-nuclear-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周早些时候，欧洲最大的核电站发生 36 小时的备用电源中断事件，联合国原子能机构再次对俄罗斯与乌克兰战争的安全风险发出警告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/iaea-cites-deep-concern-over-supply-at-ukraine-nuclear-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 05:58:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥尔班警告称，欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税可能引发“经济冷战”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/orban-warns-of-economic-cold-war-with-eu-tariffs-on-china-evs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟总理维克托·奥尔班表示，如果欧盟选择对中国电动汽车征收额外关税，欧盟将陷入“经济冷战”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/orban-warns-of-economic-cold-war-with-eu-tariffs-on-china-evs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 05:52:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本首相石破茂在国会演讲中强调抗击通货紧缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/japan-s-ishiba-emphasizes-deflation-fight-in-parliament-speech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本新首相石破茂在首次国会演讲中强调，其经济政策的首要任务是战胜通货紧缩，使日本经济走上稳定的增长轨道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/japan-s-ishiba-emphasizes-deflation-fight-in-parliament-speech</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 05:37:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克总统候选人计划通过谈判结束叛乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/mozambique-presidency-frontrunner-plans-talks-to-end-insurgency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克 10 月 9 日总统大选的执政党候选人丹尼尔·查波 (Daniel Chapo) 表示，他赞成通过谈判结束伊斯兰国支持的叛乱活动，该叛乱活动已推迟了道达尔能源公司 (TotalEnergies SE) 计划在该国东北部实施的价值 200 亿美元的液化天然气出口项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/mozambique-presidency-frontrunner-plans-talks-to-end-insurgency</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 04:56:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克称将参加特朗普在宾夕法尼亚州枪击案现场举行的集会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/musk-says-he-ll-attend-trump-rally-at-butler-pennsylvania-shooting-site</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克表示，他将参加唐纳德·特朗普周六在宾夕法尼亚州巴特勒举行的集会，该地是前总统特朗普首次遭遇暗杀的地点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/musk-says-he-ll-attend-trump-rally-at-butler-pennsylvania-shooting-site</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 04:25:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
