      <title>大手笔押注俄罗斯为散户投资者带来纸上财富</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/russia-entices-eu-and-us-retail-investors-despite-invasion-of-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里斯蒂安·韦尔 (Christian Wehr) 第一次前往俄罗斯进行投资者之旅时，带上了他的父亲，以获得精神支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/russia-entices-eu-and-us-retail-investors-despite-invasion-of-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将对中国电动汽车关税进行投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/eu-set-to-vote-on-tariffs-targeting-electric-vehicles-from-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟成员国将于周五投票决定是否对中国产电动汽车征收高达 45% 的关税，这一决定可能会进一步加剧欧盟与北京方面的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/eu-set-to-vote-on-tariffs-targeting-electric-vehicles-from-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 03:41:19 GMT</pubDate>
